Everyone dreams about winning the lottery. Not everyone is lucky enough to be the one who takes home the whole pot, with the odds being in 300 billion. But Mark and Cindy Hill, 52 and 51, became one of those few lucky people. 

And when they won the lottery, they defied the odds again by spending their money in a way no one would ever expect. 

